<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<title>Püha Taevas</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="css/base.css" media="screen" />
<!--[if lte IE 6]>
<style type="text/css">

img {
behavior:url("inc/iepngfix.htc");
}

</style>
<![endif]--> 
</head>
<body class="create">

  <div id="taevas">
    <p><a href="http://www.taevas.ee/"><span>www.taevas.ee</span></a></p>
  </div>

  <!-- #container start -->
  <div id="container">
  <div id="containerSpan">

    <!-- #header start -->
    <div id="header">

      <h1><a href="/"><span>Püha Taevas</span></a></h1>
      <div id="intro">
        <h2>Sinu ees on Püha Instrumendi pärgament. </h2>
      </div>

    </div>
    <!-- #header end -->

    <!-- #content start -->
    <div id="content">

      <div id="instruction">
        <p>Pane siia kirja oma kõige pühamad soovid ja sisemine hääl.</p>
        <p class="p2">Madalamad mörinad leiad vasakult, kõrged kilinad paremalt. Noodid sea ritta ülevalt alla, moodustades soovitud viisijupi.</p>
        <p>Kui õige lugu valmis, pane kirja oma loomingu pealkiri ja enda e-posti aadress. Nüüd ei olegi rohkem vaja, kui vajuta nuppu “Valmista” ja Taeva Püha Instrument asub tööle.</p>
        <p>Mõne hetke pärast on Sinu lugu ekraanil ja e-postkastis videojäädvustus, mida valitutega jagada.</p>
      </div>

      <form id="editor_form" action="/song" method="post">

        <div id="editor">

      <span class="letters">
        <p>C D E F G A H C D E F G A</p>
      </span>


      <% 30.times do |i| %>
        <span>
        <% @notes.each_index do |j| %>
          <input type="checkbox" name="notes[<%=i%>][<%=j%>]" value="<%=@notes.at(j)%>"  />
          <img src="/img/ball-16x16.png" class="<%=@notes.at(j)%>" />
        <% end %>
        </span>
      <% end %>



        </div>

        <div id="send">
          <table width="100%">
            <tr>
              <td><label for="fTitle">Loo pealkiri:</label></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="field"><input type="text" class="text" name="name" id="fTitle" style="width:155px;" /></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><label for="fEmail">Sinu e-post:</label></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="field"><input type="text" class="text" name="email" id="fEmail" style="width:155px;" /></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><input type="submit" class="submit" value="Valmista" /></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>

      </form>

      <div class="clearer"></div>

    </div>
    <!-- #content end -->

  </div>
  </div>
  <!-- #container end -->

  <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.3.2/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>  
  <script src="/js/flowplayer-3.1.4.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
  <script src="/js/soundmanager2.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
  <script src="/js/application.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>

</body>
</html>